			<div class="content" id="post-content-2830363">
									

<p>&#8230;shaggy, you've been a site member for four years. &gt;_&gt;</p>
<p>Either way, you don't have to be a veteran of writing to be a veteran of the site.</p>
<p>If you're writing a GoI format though, that implies that the GoI exists, and has articles about it.</p>
<p>I don't see many newbies writing a GoI format for an established GoI right out the gate, during their first few weeks/months on the site.</p>

